{"tid":95941,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"人在台中 點解google 會比奪命斜我踩","createTime":"2017-01-26T12:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T13:37:26.000Z","uid":41888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"463ab75b563bfdf3ebdbf9c447271777d581b806","tid":95941,"uid":41888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"單車環島第二日，新竹到台中  本書寫80km<br />\n<br />\n但跟google 踩 會有成100km<br />\n<br />\n比左條勁長上斜我屌  踩得10km/h 踩到幾時呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n踩左成粒鐘都係咁樣既斜路<br />\n<br />\n點解佢唔整個選項叫避開斜路<br />\n<br />\n明明已經朝早 10點半出發  最後都係天都黑晒7點<br />\n<br />\n先到住嗰度  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人知點樣避開斜路  我知普遍近海先多平路<br />\n<br />\n但係近海好似無機車單車專用線 好驚比車夾死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落去逢甲掃野食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f908a48c98c36cc2cb7a813c9572b2ba189db0bd","tid":95941,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"台中聽日落邊度"},{"pid":"9e8bc92143c650793ee77b521a671112e7e82d3a","tid":95941,"uid":41888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台中聽日落邊度</blockquote><br />\n落嘉義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3197c7cf5c214dee3ad9976e96c9fb86c8c74b15","tid":95941,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"點解唔逆時針踩..."},{"pid":"577b1299823b5f7bf3cf5f69f09ceaa3ac973cec","tid":95941,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"你踩台幾???"}]}